Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate Kiddwaya on Monday morning consoled Laycon over Erica’s disqualification. Laycon was feeling sad about her disqualification and said he will always support Erica despite their rift. Kiddwaya, responding assured him that Erica will forgive him but it would take time. According to him, housemates need each other outside the house to succeed. “With time, Erica will forgive you eventually. Because at some point, we need each other to do stuff outside the house.” DAILY POST recalls that Erica was disqualified from the BBNaija lockdown house over violence, bullying and disrespecting the rules of the house. Erica, before her exit from the house hurled insults and threatened to kill Laycon after he refused to explain to her when she tried to kiss him.